SchemaItem.Name: 00010_ExchangeRateList_Values

SchemaItem.Name: CelniSprava_GenerateExchangeRate
SchemaItem.M01:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?> <xsl:stylesheet xmlns:xsl="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Transform" version="1.0" xmlns:AS="http://schema.advantages.cz/AsapFunctions" xmlns:date="http://exslt.org/dates-and-times" exclude-result-prefixes="AS date">
<xsl:param name="newRate"/>
<xsl:template match="ROOT"> <!-- 1. kurz 1.1. do 30.1. 2. kurz 1.2. do 31.12.9999 aktuální kurz 1.2. do 31.12.9999 - existuje do 30.1.? -> ano - kurz od 1.2. již existuje aktuální kurz 1.3. do 31.12.9999 - existuje do 28.2.? -> ne - založíme kurz 1.3. do 31.12.9999 + aktuální kurz (1.2.) ukončíme na 28.2. --> <ROOT> <!-- set an existing rate to end one day before the current rate --> <xsl:apply-templates select="ExchangeRate"/> <!-- save a new rate --> <xsl:apply-templates select="$newRate/DSKurz/kurz"/> </ROOT> </xsl:template>
<xsl:template match="ExchangeRate"> <xsl:copy> <xsl:copy-of select="@*"/> <xsl:attribute name="DateTo"> <xsl:value-of select="AS:AddDays($newRate/DSKurz/kurz/OD, -1)"/> </xsl:attribute> <xsl:copy-of select="*"/> </xsl:copy> </xsl:template>
<xsl:template match="kurz"> <ExchangeRate Id="{AS:GenerateId()}" refCurrencyId="{@refCurrencyId}" DateTo="{DO}" ExchangeRate="{translate(KURZ, ',', '.')}" Unit="{POCET}" refExchangeRateListId="{@refExchangeRateListId}" /> </xsl:template> </xsl:stylesheet>

SchemaItem.Name: CelniSprava_ExtractXml
SchemaItem.M01:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?> <xsl:stylesheet xmlns:xsl="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Transform" version="1.0" xmlns:AS="http://schema.advantages.cz/AsapFunctions" xmlns:date="http://exslt.org/dates-and-times" xmlns:ds="http://tempuri.org/DSKurz.xsd" exclude-result-prefixes="AS date ds">
<xsl:param name="exchangeRateListId" select="'43b6acd4-223c-4c75-9eaa-a83da2bf100d'"/> <xsl:variable name="listId" select="AS:isnull($exchangeRateListId, AS:GetConstant('ExchangeRateList_CelniKurzy'))"/>
<xsl:template match="ROOT"> <DSKurz> <xsl:apply-templates select="AS:ToXml(AS:DecodeTextFromBase64(/ROOT/WorkQueueEntry/Data, 'UTF-8'))/ds:DSKurz/ds:kurz"/> </DSKurz> </xsl:template>
<xsl:template match="ds:kurz"> <xsl:variable name="currencyId" select="AS:LookupValue('4fa0d1fe-d309-43ff-9e0d-ad2422df6f0c', ds:MENA)"/>
<xsl:if test="string($currencyId)"> <!-- Check if the rate exists already. The rate delivered is e.g. from 1.1.2014 till 31.12.2999 and we check if we have a rate valid until 31.12.2013. In that case this new rate has been already stored. --> <xsl:variable name="existingRate" select="AS:LookupValue( 'baa51837-f69d-4449-804c-c4edfcd617ea', 'ExchangeRate_parCurrencyId', $currencyId, 'ExchangeRate_parDate', AS:AddDays(ds:OD, -1), 'ExchangeRate_parExchangeRateListId', $listId )"/> <xsl:variable name="rate" select="number(translate(ds:KURZ, ',', '.'))"/>
<xsl:if test="string($existingRate) and number($existingRate) != $rate"> <xsl:message terminate="yes"> <xsl:value-of select="concat( 'Exchange rate for currency ', ds:MENA, ' already exists for ', ds:OD, ' but the rate is different from the rate stored in the system.', ' Input rate: ', $rate, ' Existing rate: ', number($existingRate) )"/> </xsl:message> </xsl:if>
<xsl:if test="not(string($existingRate))"> <kurz> <xsl:copy-of select="@*"/> <xsl:attribute name="refCurrencyId"> <xsl:value-of select="$currencyId"/> </xsl:attribute> <xsl:attribute name="refExchangeRateListId"> <xsl:value-of select="$listId"/> </xsl:attribute> <xsl:apply-templates/> </kurz> </xsl:if> </xsl:if> </xsl:template>
<xsl:template match="ds:*"> <xsl:element name="{local-name()}"> <xsl:copy-of select="@*"/> <xsl:apply-templates/> </xsl:element> </xsl:template> </xsl:stylesheet>

SchemaItem.Name: CNB_SetDateToYesterday
SchemaItem.M01:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?> <xsl:stylesheet xmlns:xsl="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Transform" version="1.0" xmlns:AS="http://schema.advantages.cz/AsapFunctions" xmlns:date="http://exslt.org/dates-and-times" exclude-result-prefixes="AS date">
<xsl:template match="ROOT"> <ROOT> <xsl:apply-templates select="ExchangeRate"/> </ROOT> </xsl:template>
<xsl:template match="ExchangeRate"> <xsl:copy> <xsl:copy-of select="@*"/> <xsl:attribute name="DateTo"><xsl:value-of select="AS:AddDays(@DateTo, -1)"/></xsl:attribute> <xsl:copy-of select="*"/> </xsl:copy> </xsl:template> </xsl:stylesheet>

SchemaItem.Name: CNB_SaveDailyRate
SchemaItem.M01:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?> <xsl:stylesheet xmlns:xsl="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Transform" version="1.0" xmlns:AS="http://schema.advantages.cz/AsapFunctions" xmlns:date="http://exslt.org/dates-and-times" xmlns:str="http://exslt.org/strings" exclude-result-prefixes="AS date str">
<xsl:param name="exchangeRateListId"/> <xsl:variable name="listId" select="AS:isnull($exchangeRateListId, AS:GetConstant('DefaultExchangeRateList_Sales'))"/>
<xsl:template match="ROOT"> <ROOT> <xsl:apply-templates select="WorkQueueEntry"/> </ROOT> </xsl:template>
<xsl:template match="WorkQueueEntry"> <xsl:variable name="lines" select="str:split(Data, '
')"/>
<xsl:for-each select="$lines[position() > 2]"> <xsl:variable name="currencyLineSplit" select="str:split(., '|')"/> <xsl:variable name="currencyId" select="AS:LookupValue('4fa0d1fe-d309-43ff-9e0d-ad2422df6f0c', $currencyLineSplit[4])"/> <xsl:if test="string($currencyId)"> <xsl:variable name="rate" select="translate($currencyLineSplit[5], ',', '.')"/> <xsl:variable name="unit" select="$currencyLineSplit[3]"/>
<ExchangeRate Id="{AS:GenerateId()}" refCurrencyId="{$currencyId}" DateTo="{AS:AddDays(date:date(), 1)}" ExchangeRate="{$rate}" Unit="{$unit}" refExchangeRateListId="{$listId}" /> </xsl:if> </xsl:for-each> </xsl:template> </xsl:stylesheet>

SchemaItem.Name: ARES_LoadBusinessPartner
SchemaItem.M01:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?> <xsl:stylesheet xmlns:xsl="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Transform" version="1.0" xmlns:AS="http://schema.advantages.cz/AsapFunctions" xmlns:are="http://wwwinfo.mfcr.cz/ares/xml_doc/schemas/ares/ares_answer_basic/v_1.0.3" xmlns:D="http://wwwinfo.mfcr.cz/ares/xml_doc/schemas/ares/ares_datatypes/v_1.0.3" xmlns:date="http://exslt.org/dates-and-times" exclude-result-prefixes="AS date are D">
<xsl:template match="ROOT"> <ROOT> <xsl:apply-templates select="BusinessPartner"/> </ROOT> </xsl:template>
<xsl:template match="BusinessPartner"> <xsl:if test="string(@LegalRegistrationCode)"> <xsl:variable name="aresResult" select="AS:HttpRequest(concat('http://wwwinfo.mfcr.cz/cgi-bin/ares/darv_bas.cgi?ico=', @LegalRegistrationCode))"/> <xsl:variable name="aresResultXml" select="AS:ToXml($aresResult)"/> <xsl:variable name="error" select="$aresResultXml/are:Ares_odpovedi/are:Odpoved/D:E/D:ET"/> <xsl:variable name="zaklad" select="$aresResultXml/are:Ares_odpovedi/are:Odpoved/D:VBAS"/> <xsl:variable name="address" select="$zaklad/D:AA"/>
<xsl:if test="string($error)"> <xsl:message terminate="yes"><xsl:value-of select="$error"/></xsl:message> </xsl:if>
<xsl:copy> <xsl:copy-of select="@*"/> <xsl:attribute name="TaxIdentificationCode"><xsl:value-of select="$zaklad/D:DIC"/></xsl:attribute> <xsl:copy-of select="*[name() != 'Name' and name() != 'BusinessPartnerCommunicationChannel']"/> <Name><xsl:value-of select="$zaklad/D:OF"/></Name>
<xsl:choose> <xsl:when test="count(BusinessPartnerCommunicationChannel[ @refBusinessPartnerCommunicationChannelTypeId = AS:GetConstant('BusinessPartnerCommunicationChannelType_AddressLegal') ]) = 0">
<BusinessPartnerCommunicationChannel Id="{AS:GenerateId()}" refBusinessPartnerCommunicationChannelTypeId="{ AS:GetConstant('BusinessPartnerCommunicationChannelType_AddressLegal')}" > <xsl:call-template name="SetAddress"> <xsl:with-param name="address" select="$address"/> </xsl:call-template> </BusinessPartnerCommunicationChannel> </xsl:when> <xsl:otherwise> <xsl:apply-templates select="BusinessPartnerCommunicationChannel[ @refBusinessPartnerCommunicationChannelTypeId = AS:GetConstant('BusinessPartnerCommunicationChannelType_AddressLegal') ]"> <xsl:with-param name="address" select="$address"/> </xsl:apply-templates> </xsl:otherwise> </xsl:choose> </xsl:copy> </xsl:if> </xsl:template>
<xsl:template match="BusinessPartnerCommunicationChannel"> <xsl:param name="address"/>
<xsl:copy> <xsl:copy-of select="@*"/> <xsl:call-template name="SetAddress"> <xsl:with-param name="address" select="$address"/> </xsl:call-template> <xsl:copy-of select="*"/> </xsl:copy> </xsl:template>
<xsl:template name="SetAddress"> <xsl:param name="address"/>
<xsl:attribute name="Street1"><xsl:value-of select="$address/D:NU"/></xsl:attribute> <xsl:attribute name="HouseNumber"><xsl:value-of select="$address/D:CD"/></xsl:attribute> <xsl:attribute name="PostalCode"><xsl:value-of select="$address/D:PSC"/></xsl:attribute> <xsl:attribute name="City"><xsl:value-of select="$address/D:N"/></xsl:attribute> </xsl:template> </xsl:stylesheet>

SchemaItem.Name: CNB_LoadDailyRate
SchemaItem.M01:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?> <xsl:stylesheet xmlns:xsl="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Transform" version="1.0" xmlns:AS="http://schema.advantages.cz/AsapFunctions" xmlns:date="http://exslt.org/dates-and-times" xmlns:str="http://exslt.org/strings" exclude-result-prefixes="AS date str">
<xsl:param name="lastState"/>
<xsl:template match="/"> <xsl:variable name="cnb" select="AS:HttpRequest('http://www.cnb.cz/cs/financni_trhy/devizovy_trh/kurzy_devizoveho_trhu/denni_kurz.txt')"/> <xsl:if test="$lastState != substring-before($cnb, ' ')"> <ROOT> <File> <Name><xsl:value-of select="substring-before($cnb, '
')"/></Name> <Data> <xsl:value-of select="$cnb"/> </Data> </File> </ROOT> </xsl:if> </xsl:template> </xsl:stylesheet>
